Need for spring boot
    Spring Framework = Powerful but heavy, manual setup.
    Spring Boot = Lightweight, auto-configured, fast development, production-ready.

Servlets
    Servlets in Java are server-side Java programs that handle client requests (like HTTP GET/POST), process them, and 
    generate dynamic responses. They run inside a web container (e.g., Tomcat) and form the backbone of Java web applications.
LifeCycle of servlet 
    Init = setup, Service = request handling, Destroy = cleanup.

